{"tid":913891,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人在江湖","createTime":"2018-11-23T17:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T01:16:25.000Z","uid":116455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3efdce306b86cbc271c3eda01e7f4f9e6d7dc7","tid":913891,"uid":116455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:56:03.000Z","msg":"成為江湖一份子前，請先回答以下問題及分配初始屬性。<br />\n<br />\n根骨<br />\n悟性<br />\n心志<br />\n福緣<br />\n力道<br />\n身法<br />\n魅力<br />\n<br />\n以上7項皆不能低於1，換言之，你將有43點作自由分配，總點數為50。<br />\n<br />\n1. 你認為你的出生應該如何?<br />\n<br />\na) 富甲一方<br />\nb) 窮困市民<br />\nc) 武林世家<br />\nd) 山中遊俠<br />\n<br />\n2. 你夢想成為那一種人?<br />\n<br />\na) 正道大俠<br />\nb) 意欲一統江湖的一代梟雄<br />\nc) 無惡不作的魔頭<br />\nc) 逍遙一生的浪子<br />\n<br />\n3. 你認為你擅長那一類的武功?<br />\n<br />\na) 劍法<br />\nb) 刀法<br />\nc) 拳掌<br />\nd) 指法<br />\ne) 暗器<br />\nf) 奇門<br />\ng) 每項皆平平無奇<br />\n<br />\n4. 如果面臨死亡，你認為一生中最捨不得之事為何事?<br />\n<br />\n請自由作答"},{"pid":"4a94ae08e2524c45be662ad215d985dddeb0a527","tid":913891,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:57:05.000Z","msg":"身不由己"},{"pid":"d6052b8b70d220a15cadcc6e367faa3cb207d970","tid":913891,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T17:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://instagram.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/vp/7b4c465b0ecbdd08221025b2fc4d6bc1/5C729CA6/t51.2885-15/e35/44746793_347734682439567_3246828082073909745_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fvp%2F7b4c465b0ecbdd08221025b2fc4d6bc1%2F5C729CA6%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F44746793_347734682439567_3246828082073909745_n.jpg&h=dd8153de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://instagram.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/vp/08f46af63317691a3ea59fd8beb2f37f/5CAF5EC5/t51.2885-15/e35/44736194_544549362636560_3518584945590385428_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fvp%2F08f46af63317691a3ea59fd8beb2f37f%2F5CAF5EC5%2Ft51.2885-15%2F